
"Their talking about the business right now and that your going to take over it as soon as you turn 18," she told me.
"That's so soon."
"But your the rightful heir."
I turned around and saw Lia's dad coming out the room with some other guy in a suit.
The guy nodded hello to me before shaking hands with Lia's dad and left
"Ashton, how have you been?" Lia's dad asked giving me a hug.
"I'm fine," I replied, "so tell me everything, Ken."
